  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add chickpeas, norwegian glaze, fish broth, and thyme to the pot.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the stew until it is partially smooth.",
    "Stir in heavy cream, if using, and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Season the stew with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs, if desired."
